y":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:51:52.000Z","msg":"Is 5000萬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:33:50.000Z","msg":"屌牙，一直以為係3000萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1651c68d0c07e5f906b47bcac66fea463563ba62","tid":2274061,"uid":290118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:34:43.000Z","msg":"等睇惡犬入嚟吠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"724468afd04703486bdeef97e6beb02d29049640","tid":2274061,"uid":72795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:38:44.000Z","msg":"又會咁啱有記者影到正面send番張相俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肯定係天選之人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（利申：課咗一個月糧，感恩為全人類出頭）"},{"pid":"7e984bc4ac0cb72158d0d8e03c5238f1fc5b2fcf","tid":2274061,"uid":59158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:43:49.000Z","msg":"感謝你既付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n攬炒吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"584b8aea31da2a7198960808381626f71327a0b6","tid":2274061,"uid":24924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:52:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be51253231cf6ef616074d1f5194f0821b488426","tid":2274061,"uid":314184,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T14:16:12.000Z","msg":"好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b304599308f7b870001e61c36b7bbdff974c20","tid":2274061,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22977c8447052c4005d56d2beddd76a0c93e3e95","tid":2274061,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T07:38:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/7fJ8MP20copy_Vqdkl_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F7fJ8MP20copy_Vqdkl_1200x0.png&h=57956875&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年 1 月 1 日元旦大遊行晚上，銅鑼灣的大圍捕，劉祖廸被捕<br />\n<br />\n今年 27 歲的「攬炒巴」在過去一年來從事國際遊說工作，今年 8 月被警方通緝。上月他終於公開身份，以「劉祖廸」真面目示人。<br />\n<br />\n日夜為香港政局著急的劉祖廸，其實從來不喜歡待在香港。在大學畢業後，他就希望可以周遊列國，每三年到一個新的國家體驗生活。去年 6 月反送中運動爆發，他當時仍身處英國。當香港示威現場煙霧彌漫之際，他坐在電腦鍵盤前敲出一篇篇的連登帖文、外媒投稿，大談他推動國際線的策略。<br />\n<br />\n他深感自己身處英國安然寫的論述，影響了不少的香港人抗爭，有時難免自責，「覺得自己滿手鮮血」。幾個月後他患上嚴重抑鬱，最教他鬱鬱寡歡的，是不能回港抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n去年 12 月他毅然踏上回港的航機，走到抗爭現場抑鬱好轉不少。他元旦在街頭被捕，與很多抗爭者一樣在警署待了 48 小時。<br />\n<br />\n「死過翻生，我一定珍惜呢個機會。」如今流亡英國，他堅持推動國際線「光復故鄉」，即使在英國遇襲亦無懼，「始終要有人堅持去行落去，死就死」。<br />\n<br />\n*     *     *     *     *<br />\n<br />\n上個月初，攬炒巴終於公開真身，影片中他正式介紹自己的全名「劉祖廸」（Finn）。但其實早在 8 月，多間建制傳媒已經公開他的全名，報道他被通緝的消息。<br />\n<br />\n他一口氣開了 Facebook 專頁、Twitter 和 Instagram，專頁不忘在全名前，標示自己「攬炒巴」這個廣為人知的身份。簡介上他介紹真實的自己，是一名 90 後、抗爭者、還有「為了光復故鄉而流亡海外」。他正職是一名測量師，穿起筆直的西裝，看起來是個年青有為的年輕人。專頁亦提供任何人都可以聯絡他的途徑，一改以往安全、低調行事的作風。<br />\n<br />\n由連登上的「我要攬炒」，到公開真實身份，只是短短 1 年多的時間，他不是無想過身份會曝光，只是 8.10 的國安法大圍捕和翌日被通緝，推前了一切的計劃：「只能夠講，係一個唔到我控制的轉變。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E6%83%A6%E5%BF%B5%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%87%B4%E6%8A%91%E9%AC%B1-%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E5%8D%B3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E6%94%AC%E7%82%92%E5%B7%B4-%E6%AD%BB%E9%81%8E%E7%BF%BB%E7%94%9F%E7%BA%8C%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E6%2583%25A6%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%2587%25B4%25E6%258A%2591%25E9%25AC%25B1-%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E5%258D%25B3%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E6%2594%25AC%25E7%2582%2592%25E5%25B7%25B4-%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%2F&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9rP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=47b9cb7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E8%25A8%25AA-%25E6%2583%25A6%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%2587%25B4%25E6%258A%2591%25E9%25AC%25B1-%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E5%258D%25B3%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E6%2594%25AC%25E7%2582%2592%25E5%25B7%25B4-%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%25BF%25BB%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%25BA%258C%25E5%2585%2589%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%2F&h=3fcef6db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%B0%88%E8%A8%AA-%E6%83%A6%E5%BF%B5%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%87%B4%E6%8A%91%E9%AC%B1-%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E5%8D%B3%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E6%94%AC%E7%82%92%E5%B7%B4-%E6%AD%BB%E9%81%8E%E7%BF%BB%E7%94%9F%E7%BA%8C%E5%85%89%E5%BE%A9%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T15:51:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}